{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":32,"arguments_yes_count":0,"arguments_no_count":5,"id":496,"created_at":"2015-10-09T14:53:21+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-09T14:53:21+0200","body":"<p>Afin de lutter contre l&#39;envoi massif de courriel, une taxe sera cr&eacute;&eacute;e pour tout envoi en tr&egrave;s grand noimbre&nbsp; de courriels similaires.&nbsp; Le montant de la taxe, le nombre de courriels identiques consid&eacute;r&eacute; comme un envoi massif et le taux de similarit&eacute; des courriels feront l&#39;objet d&#39;un d&eacute;cret minist&eacute;riel.<\/p>","versions_count":0,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":5,"author":{"username":"Pierre Lescanne","displayName":"Pierre Lescanne","uniqueId":"pierrelescanne","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/pierrelescanne","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":87,"title":"Section 2","subtitle":"Service public de la donn\u00e9e","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[{"isContribuable":false,"id":6123,"body":"Pas besoin d'une taxe, les citoyens s'organisent d\u00e9j\u00e0 et mettent en place des solutions.","created_at":"2015-10-18T22:17:00+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-18T22:17:00+0200","is_enabled":true,"votes_count":0,"type":0,"is_trashed":false,"author":{"username":"Ludovic Marchal","displayName":"Ludovic Marchal","uniqueId":"ludovicmarchal","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/02\/1053_default_avatar.png"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/ludovicmarchal","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-pro